        </p>

        <p>
            <a href="#" class="button button--green">Accept</a>
            <a href="#" class="button button--red">Decline</a>
        </p>

        <p>
            I hope you choose to accept the rent, otherwise please let {{ renter_name | raw }} know. If it doesnâ€™t fit your schedule, or you need the item that particular day.
